CodeDef lower Filter
CodeDef lower Alias lc

CodeDef lc Filter
CodeDef lc Description Lower case
CodeDef lc Routine <<EOR
sub {
	use locale;
	if ($Scratch->{mv_locale}) {
	    POSIX::setlocale(LC_CTYPE, $Scratch->{mv_locale});
	}
	return lc(shift);
}
EOR
